data.description: Welcome Home. This beautifully maintained 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath is located in the quiet neighborhood of Prairie Hollow in Ingalls, in the Pendleton school district. This home has been lovingly cared for by a single owner, and has never been home to any pets. Only 1.5 miles from the heart of downtown Fortville and 10 minutes to downtown Pendleton, you'll enjoy the old town charm but always have something to do, with the area booming with new businesses and growth. New features in the home include a fresh coat of paint throughout, a new dishwasher, new front door and storm door, new light fixtures and faucets, and 2" blinds. The backyard has a delightful surprise beyond the patio- beautiful landscaping and fruit bearing pear trees!
